title: She May, She Might
lyrics:
She may
She might
Too bad [?]
She'll try
She might

Sometimes

To find a way outside

Her mind



Too much

She sighs

To say well who would want to say goodbye



She may

She might

Some day

[?]



[Chorus]

Not now, not today

Who got you in its way



She may

She might

For now, prefer to spend the day inside



She hears

Not quite

Your voice [?] to reply



She knows

By sight

Too well

All that's being left behind



[Chorus]

Not now, not today

Run, run, run away



She may

She might

[?]



She may

She might

[?] another time



She may

She might

Today
